snippet.title: Adam Post
snippet.description: ADAM POST, nickname "HALF SPEED TUCCI".   Creator and editor of several comic book projects including COLLEGE OF THE DEAD, THE CHROMIUM MAN, and the TRIUMPHANT COMIC BOOK UNIVERSE, VAMPIRE GIRLS, DREAM ANGEL, the Personality Comics line of biographical comic books and the line of parody super hero comics SPOOF COMICS.
